OL,3,CNHS plea to keep hospitals smoke-free
OL,4,Cafter discarded cigarette delays A&E
OL,6,FA hospital trust in Nottingham is
OL,7,Fasking the public to support their
OL,8,Fplea to stop all smoking on their
OL,9,Fsites, following a fire that began
OL,10,Ffrom a discarded cigarette.
OL,12,FNottingham University Hospitals NHS
OL,13,FTrust (NUH) says the buildings and
OL,14,Fgrounds of the Queens Medical Centre,
OL,15,FNottingham City Hospital and Ropewalk
OL,16,FHouse have been smoke-free since 2006.
