OL,3,CNHS plea to keep hospitals smoke-free
OL,4,Cafter discarded cigarette delays A&E
OL,6,FA number of local crews attended a
OL,7,Fblaze on the 2nd January this year at
OL,8,Fthe Queens Medical Centre in Lenton,
OL,9,Fwhich was located in the structural
OL,10,Fvoid.
OL,12,FThe fire caused delays in the
OL,13,Fhospital's day-to-day operations with
OL,14,Fsome patients relocated, and Accident
OL,15,Fand Emergency admissions were
OL,16,Ftemporarily paused.
OL,18,FTom Jenkinson, Emergency and Acute
OL,19,FCare General Manager, said:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
