OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F379A1769900573
OL,3,CNHS plea to keep hospitals smoke-free
OL,4,Cafter discarded cigarette delays A&E
OL,6,F"The incident meant a small number of
OL,7,Fpatients were relocated as a
OL,8,Fprecaution and we temporarily paused
OL,9,Fadmissions into A&E whilst the
OL,10,FNottinghamshire Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService assessed the situation.
OL,13,F"We are grateful for the support given
OL,14,Fto us by the Nottinghamshire Fire and
OL,15,FRescue Service (NFRS) and thankful
OL,16,Fthat no patients or staff came to
OL,17,Fharm."
