OL,3,CNHS plea to keep hospitals smoke-free
OL,4,Cafter discarded cigarette delays A&E
OL,6,FThe trust is reminding the public that
OL,7,Fanyone wanting to smoke must leave
OL,8,Ftheir hospital grounds completely to
OL,9,Fdo do, including entrances, walkways,
OL,10,Fcar parks, and green spaces.
OL,12,F"Vulnerable patients at risk"
OL,14,FJack Adlam, Director of Communications
OL,15,Fand Engagement, said:
OL,17,F"Our hospitals have been smokefree for
OL,18,Fthe past two decades, but people
OL,19,Fcontinue to smoke on our hospital
OL,20,Fgrounds, particularly around our main
OL,21,Fentrances.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
