OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F379A1769900573
OL,3,CNHS plea to keep hospitals smoke-free
OL,4,Cafter discarded cigarette delays A&E
OL,6,F"For the patients, visitors and staff
OL,7,Fwho use our hospitals every day, this
OL,8,Fcreates an unpleasant and unhealthy
OL,9,Fenvironment, and it is simply
OL,10,Funacceptable.
OL,12,F"The risks of smoking to our own
OL,13,Fhealth, and the health of those around
OL,14,Fus, are well known.
OL,16,F"But this incident shows the potential
OL,17,Fdangers on a much wider and more
OL,18,Fserious scale.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
