OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F379A1769900573
OL,3,CNHS plea to keep hospitals smoke-free
OL,4,Cafter discarded cigarette delays A&E
OL,6,F"A single discarded cigarette has the
OL,7,Fability to cause a fire that could put
OL,8,Fvulnerable patients at risk, disrupt
OL,9,Fvital services, and divert our teams
OL,10,Ffrom the care they are here to provide
OL,11,F....
OL,13,F"We need everyone's support to respect
OL,14,Four smokefree policy and help us stamp
OL,15,Fout smoking on our hospital grounds."
OL,17,FThe trust says vaping is allowed on
OL,18,Ftheir grounds because they say it is
OL,19,F95% less harmful than smoking, and
OL,20,Fcontains a fraction of the chemicals
OL,21,Ffound in tobacco.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
