OL,6,FStaff say anyone found to continually
OL,7,Fbreach the the no-smoking rules could
OL,8,Fmean they are asked to leave the
OL,9,Fgrounds.
OL,11,FThe trust says it's working on a
OL,12,Fnumber of measures to reduce smoking
OL,13,Fon-site, including:
OL,15,FFor inpatients who smoke, the trust
OL,16,Fsays there are support services that
OL,17,Finclude nicotine replacement therapy
OL,18,F(NRT) and a referral to a community
OL,19,Fbased 12week stopsmoking programme.
